Bank of America Winter Village at Bryant Park is Manhattan&rsquo;s winter wonderland. Enjoy New York City&rsquo;s only free admission ice skating rink, the Holiday Shops, and rinkside dining.&nbsp;
The holiday market is open Mondays through Fridays, 11am-8pm, and Saturdays and Sundays, 10am-8pm.
The Winter Village is open through March 2, 2025, but the holiday market closes on January 5th.&nbsp;

